beer.beer_description: Cricketers Arms Scorcher Summer Ale is a new Golden Ale, using brewing techniques similar to our popular Spearhead Pale Ale. We add three specialty malts and double hop using a combination of Galaxy and our signature hop Amarillo, to deliver a non-filtered cloudy ale with citrus and tropical aromas. The perfect way to handle any scorcher over summer. In appreciation of those who slog it out over the Australian summer, Scorcher Summer Ale was crafted to refresh.
